sentences.en: Some netizens are relentless in their resentment of her. Even her micro blog followers received warnings to stay away from the "quisling".
sentences.cn: 一些网民无情地对她发泄心中的怒火，她微博的一些粉丝甚至收到了警告，叫她的粉丝远离张铭依这个“卖国贼”。

sentences.en: You know, there's a new biography of quisling.
sentences.cn: 最近有本关于卖国贼的新书。
